The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Briefs
                                                                                                               BRIEFS
                  
	Haldia, Feb. 16: The Citu union at the Indian Oil (IOC) refinery here today called a days strike on March 5 to press for equal pay for cont- ract workers and per-manent staff for the same kind of jobs. The company said production wouldnt be affected.         
	Santiniketan: Visva-Bharati teachers have decided to socially boycott the VC for allegedly cold-shouldering them at a meeting. The VC said he had asked them to give their demand  to implement a proposed pay hike  in writing.                                                                                                                                                                       
